body:
The Event-based track-TrackingParticle associators were introduced in #7175. This PR migrates the remaining references (either in configuration or code) to old-style track associators to the new-style, and finally removes the old-style associators, in order to avoid confusion and to reduce maintenance burden (e.g. in #8540 I fixed only the new-style associators).

No regression expected, none observed. Tested in CMSSW_7_5_X_2015-03-24-1100, but rebased on top of CMSSW_7_5_X_2015-03-31-2300 (due to a merge conflict).

@rovere @VinInn
